      • newListAssertInstance

        protected <E> AbstractListAssert<?,List<? extends E>,E,ObjectAssert<E>> newListAssertInstance(List<? extends E> newActual)
        从类复制的说明: AbstractObjectArrayAssert
        Create a friendly soft or "hard" assertion.

        Implementations need to redefine it so that some methods, such as AbstractObjectArrayAssert.extracting(Extractor), are able to build the appropriate list assert (eg: ListAssert versus ProxyableListAssert).

        The default implementation will assume that this concrete implementation is NOT a soft assertion.

        覆盖:
        newListAssertInstance 在类中 AbstractObjectArrayAssert<ProxyableObjectArrayAssert<ELEMENT>,ELEMENT>
        类型参数:
        E - the type of elements.
        参数:
        newActual - new value
        返回:
        a new AbstractListAssert.
